              "id": "QUE57024",
              "question": "Phineas walks out of his office and into the conference room. However, after he leaves his office, he forgets what he was coming into the conference room for. According to the encoding specificity hypothesis, what should Phineas do to regain his lost memory?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
